APOLLO_SV_00000032

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?term FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/APOLLO_SV> WHERE {
        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/APOLLO_SV_00000032>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).
            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .
            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/APOLLO_SV> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/APOLLO_SV_00000032>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_17980>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_22715>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_24780>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .

                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }

        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_26979>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_27171>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?term FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_29133>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).
            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .
            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_33308>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_33579>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_33833>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_33839>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).
            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .
            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_35259>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_35868>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_35972>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

DESCENDANTS OF polyatomic entity

{1: {'uri': u'CHEBI_25367', 'name': u'molecule'}, 2: {'uri': u'CHEBI_36358', 'name': u'polyatomic ion'}, 3: {'uri': u'CHEBI_37577', 'name': u'heteroatomic molecular entity'}, 4: {'uri': u'CHEBI_50967', 'name': u'non-covalently-bound molecular entity'}, 5: {'uri': u'CHEBI_50795', 'name': u'nanostructure'}, 6: {'uri': u'CHEBI_33839', 'name': u'macromolecule'}, 7: {'uri': u'CHEBI_33731', 'name': u'cluster'}}



    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_36357>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_36963>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_38163>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_38179>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_46081>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_50860>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF organic molecular entity

{1: {'uri': u'CHEBI_50860'}, 2: {'uri': u'CHEBI_33582', 'name': u'carbon group molecular entity'}, 3: {'uri': u'CHEBI_33675', 'name': u'p-block molecular entity'}, 4: {'uri': u'CHEBI_33579', 'name': u'main group molecular entity'}, 5: {'uri': u'CHEBI_23367', 'name': u'molecular entity'}, 6: {'uri': u'CHEBI_24431', 'name': u'chemical entity'}}

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_60004>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_60911>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

{1: {'uri': u'CHEBI_60911'}, 2: {'uri': u'CHEBI_60004', 'name': u'mixture'}, 3: {'uri': u'CHEBI_59999', 'name': u'chemical substance'}, 4: {'uri': u'CHEBI_24431', 'name': u'chemical entity'}}

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CHEBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_72695>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF organic molecule

{1: {'uri': u'CHEBI_72695'}, 2: {'uri': u'CHEBI_50860', 'name': u'organic molecular entity'}, 3: {'uri': u'CHEBI_33582', 'name': u'carbon group molecular entity'}, 4: {'uri': u'CHEBI_33675', 'name': u'p-block molecular entity'}, 5: {'uri': u'CHEBI_33579', 'name': u'main group molecular entity'}, 6: {'uri': u'CHEBI_23367', 'name': u'molecular entity'}, 7: {'uri': u'CHEBI_24431', 'name': u'chemical entity'}}

    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/CLO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CLO_0000001>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000004>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF physiological observation from clinical study data item

{1: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000004'}, 2: {'uri': u'IAO_0000027', 'name': u'data item'}, 3: {'uri': u'IAO_0000030', 'name': u'information content entity'}, 4: {'uri': u'BFO_0000031', 'name': u'generically dependent continuant'}, 5: {'uri': u'BFO_0000002', 'name': u'continuant'}, 6: {'uri': u'BFO_0000001', 'name': u'entity'}, 7: {'uri': u'owl#Thing'}}

        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000015>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).

            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }
    

DESCENDANTS OF metabolic potential drug-drug interaction

{1: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000017', 'name': u'metabolism inhibition potential drug-drug interaction'}, 2: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000018', 'name': u'metabolism induction potential drug-drug interaction'}}



    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000015>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000025>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF bioavailability measurement datum

{1: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000025'}, 2: {'uri': u'IAO_0000032', 'name': u'scalar measurement datum'}, 3: {'uri': u'IAO_0000109', 'name': u'measurement datum'}, 4: {'uri': u'IAO_0000027', 'name': u'data item'}, 5: {'uri': u'IAO_0000030', 'name': u'information content entity'}, 6: {'uri': u'BFO_0000031', 'name': u'generically dependent continuant'}, 7: {'uri': u'BFO_0000002', 'name': u'continuant'}, 8: {'uri': u'BFO_0000001', 'name': u'entity'}, 9: {'uri': u'owl#Thing'}}

    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?term FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000039>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).
            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .
            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }
    
ATTN: no DESCENDANT query results for label: primary total clearance enzyme role


    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000039>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?term FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000059>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).
            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .
            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }
    
ATTN: no DESCENDANT query results for label: evidence information from transport protein identification experiment


    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000059>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF evidence information from transport protein identification experiment

{1: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000059'}, 2: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000053', 'name': u'evidence information content entity'}, 3: {'uri': u'IAO_0000030', 'name': u'information content entity'}, 4: {'uri': u'BFO_0000031', 'name': u'generically dependent continuant'}, 5: {'uri': u'BFO_0000002', 'name': u'continuant'}, 6: {'uri': u'BFO_0000001', 'name': u'entity'}, 7: {'uri': u'owl#Thing'}}

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000069>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF evidence information from CYP450 human microsome drug metabolism identification experiment using antibody inhibitors

{1: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000069'}, 2: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000053', 'name': u'evidence information content entity'}, 3: {'uri': u'IAO_0000030', 'name': u'information content entity'}, 4: {'uri': u'BFO_0000031', 'name': u'generically dependent continuant'}, 5: {'uri': u'BFO_0000002', 'name': u'continuant'}, 6: {'uri': u'BFO_0000001', 'name': u'entity'}, 7: {'uri': u'owl#Thing'}}

DIDEO_00000070

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?term FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000070>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).
            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .
            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }
    
ATTN: no DESCENDANT query results for label: evidence information from CYP450 metabolic enzyme inhibition experiment

ATTN: no DESCENDANT query results for label: evidence information from CYP450 recombinant drug metabolism inhibition experiment


    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000080>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000093>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?term FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000104>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).
            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .
            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }
    
ATTN: no DESCENDANT query results for label: evidence information from p-glycoprotein transport protein identification experiment


    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000104>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF evidence information from p-glycoprotein transport protein identification experiment

{1: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000104'}, 2: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000053', 'name': u'evidence information content entity'}, 3: {'uri': u'IAO_0000030', 'name': u'information content entity'}, 4: {'uri': u'BFO_0000031', 'name': u'generically dependent continuant'}, 5: {'uri': u'BFO_0000002', 'name': u'continuant'}, 6: {'uri': u'BFO_0000001', 'name': u'entity'}, 7: {'uri': u'owl#Thing'}}

    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000114>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF evidence information from OATP1B1 inhibition experiment

{1: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000114'}, 2: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000053', 'name': u'evidence information content entity'}, 3: {'uri': u'IAO_0000030', 'name': u'information content entity'}, 4: {'uri': u'BFO_0000031', 'name': u'generically dependent continuant'}, 5: {'uri': u'BFO_0000002', 'name': u'continuant'}, 6: {'uri': u'BFO_0000001', 'name': u'entity'}, 7: {'uri': u'owl#Thing'}}

DIDEO_00000152

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?term FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000152>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).
            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .
            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }
    
ATTN: no DESCENDANT query results for label: freshly isolated human hepatocyte population


    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000152>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF freshly isolated human hepatocyte population

    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?term FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000163>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).
            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .
            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }
    
ATTN: no DESCENDANT query results for label: individual human intestinal microsomal fraction


    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000163>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF individual human intestinal microsomal fraction

    SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?term FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000173>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).
            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .
            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }
    
ATTN: no DESCENDANT query results for label: nifedipine dehydrogenation


    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000173>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF nifedipine dehydrogenation

{1: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000173'}, 2: {'uri': u'MOP_0000590', 'name': u'dehydrogenation'}, 3: {'uri': u'BFO_0000015', 'name': u'process'}, 4: {'uri': u'BFO_0000003', 'name': u'occurrent'}, 5: {'uri': u'BFO_0000001', 'name': u'entity'}, 6: {'uri': u'owl#Thing'}}

    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DIDEO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DIDEO_00000183>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF recombinant protein production host role

{1: {'uri': u'DIDEO_00000183'}, 2: {'uri': u'OBI_0000444', 'name': u'target of material addition role'}, 3: {'uri': u'BFO_0000023', 'name': u'role'}, 4: {'uri': u'BFO_0000017', 'name': u'realizable entity'}, 5: {'uri': u'BFO_0000020', 'name': u'specifically dependent continuant'}, 6: {'uri': u'BFO_0000002', 'name': u'continuant'}, 7: {'uri': u'BFO_0000001', 'name': u'entity'}, 8: {'uri': u'owl#Thing'}}

'name': u'fluticasone / vilanterol Dry Powder Inhaler'}, 1976: {'uri': u'DRON_00731692', 'name': u'hyaluronate / mecobalamin Oral Lozenge'}, 1977: {'uri': u'DRON_00731700', 'name': u'Morphine Cartridge'}, 1978: {'uri': u'DRON_00731703', 'name': u'Guaifenesin Oral Powder'}, 1979: {'uri': u'DRON_00731705', 'name': u'Penicillin V Oral Granules'}, 1980: {'uri': u'DRON_00731707', 'name': u'potassium bicarbonate Oral Granules'}, 1981: {'uri': u'DRON_00731711', 'name': u'Regular Insulin, Human Pen Injector'}}



    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/DRON> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DRON_00000005>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
    
ANCESTORS OF drug product

    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/ERO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ERO_0001209>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/GO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0008150>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/GO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0032991>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .

        }
    }

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/GO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0043234>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

        {
            ?term rdfs:subClassOf ?s .
            FILTER (?s = <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0044237>)
            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).
            OPTIONAL {?term rdfs:label ?label} .
            OPTIONAL {?subTerm rdfs:subClassOf ?term}
        }
    }

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/GO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0051051>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/GO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0003824>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }

        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).

        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MOP_0001385>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000029>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/OBI> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000192>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000968>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>

        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0500001>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

            FILTER (isIRI(?term)).

        }

ATTN: no DESCENDANT query results for label: active ingredient quantification specification


    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/PDRO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PDRO_0000124>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)

unit'}, 32: {'uri': u'UO_0000261', 'name': u'conduction unit'}, 33: {'uri': u'UO_0000315', 'name': u'turbidity unit'}, 34: {'uri': u'UO_0000047', 'name': u'area unit'}, 35: {'uri': u'UO_0000045', 'name': u'base unit'}, 36: {'uri': u'UO_0000127', 'name': u'radiation unit'}, 37: {'uri': u'UO_0000157', 'name': u'light unit'}, 38: {'uri': u'UO_0000186', 'name': u'dimensionless unit'}}



    PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
    SELECT ?path ?label ?link FROM <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/merged/UO> WHERE {
        {
            SELECT ?s ?o ?label WHERE {
                {
                    ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                } UNION {
                    ?s owl:equivalentClass ?s1 .
                    ?s1 owl:intersectionOf ?s2 .
                    ?s2 rdf:first ?o  .
                    FILTER (isIRI(?o))
                    OPTIONAL {?o rdfs:label ?label}
                }
                FILTER ( ?s != ?o )
            }
        }
        OPTION (TRANSITIVE, t_in(?s), t_out(?o), t_step (?s) as ?link, t_step ('path_id') as ?path).
        FILTER (isIRI(?o)).
        FILTER (?s= <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UO_0000000>)
    } ORDER BY DESC (?path)
